snippet.title: 10 to LIFE
snippet.description: Hi everyone! My name is Annie Elise and welcome to my channel, 10 to Life! By day, I'm a trend forecaster in the fashion industry and by night, I'm a true crime enthusiast. I highlight key true crime cases on YouTube in an effort to bring awareness to unsolved cases, create conversations for ongoing investigations, and quite frankly expose some of the evilest and heartless people on this planet.
